# Cloudflare Pages SPA fall-through.
#
# Every unmatched path is rewritten (status 200, not a 30x redirect) to
# /index.html so React Router and Clerk's path-based sub-routes
# (/sign-in/sso-callback, /sign-in/factor-two, ...) work after a hard
# refresh or direct link.  Static assets and /api/* are served as-is.
/*    /index.html   200
